OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784036893
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police now leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Ann Widdecombe's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FCounter Terrorism Police (CTP) are now
OL,8,Fleading the investigation into the
OL,9,Fdeath of former MP Ann Widdecombe, it
OL,10,Fhas been announced.
OL,12,FThe head of UK counter-terrorism
OL,13,Fpolicing, Laurence Taylor, said on
OL,14,FMonday that new information and
OL,15,Fevidence had come to light during the
OL,16,Fpolice investigation into her murder.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
