OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784036893
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police now leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Ann Widdecombe's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe 78-year-old was found dead in her
OL,8,Fhome in Haytor, Devon on Thursday
OL,9,Fmorning and Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,10,Flaunched a murder investigation on
OL,11,FFriday.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FA 28-year-old white British man from
OL,19,FRotherham, South Yorkshire, was
OL,20,Farrested on suspicion of murder on
OL,21,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784036893
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police now leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Ann Widdecombe's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHe has since be re-arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of commission, preparation
OL,9,For instigation of acts of terrorism,
OL,10,FCTP said.
OL,12,FCCTV footage of the suspect, obtained
OL,13,Fby The Sun, appears to show him
OL,14,Fgetting into a red car with a wooden
OL,15,Fstick in his pocket hours before
OL,16,Fpolice believe Widdecombe was killed.
OL,18,FAdditional footage shows the
OL,19,Fsubsequent police raid in Rotheram
OL,20,Fthat lead to the suspect's arrest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
