PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784036893
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police now leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Ann Widdecombe's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FCCTV footage, obtained by The Sun,
OL,8,Fshows the suspect being arrested in
OL,9,FRotheram over the weekend, as ITV
OL,10,FNews' Sam Holder reports
OL,12,FThe Home Secretary said she has spoken
OL,13,Fto the head of CTP and confirmed that
OL,14,Fthey are "now leading on the
OL,15,Finvestigation into the horrific murder
OL,16,Fof Ann Widdecombe".
OL,18,FIn a post of social media, Shabana
OL,19,FMahmood said she will update the House
OL,20,Fof Commons "this afternoon".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
