CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784036893
OL,3,CCounter-terrorism police now leading
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Ann Widdecombe's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the prime minister
OL,8,Fsaid it was important not to speculate
OL,9,Fon this case and said that it was
OL,10,Fimportant the integrity of this
OL,11,Finvestigation is supported.
OL,13,FHe urged anyone with any information
OL,14,Fto share it with the police.
OL,16,FInformation, images or footage can be
OL,17,Freported via the Major Incident Public
OL,18,FPortal or to Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,19,Fon 101.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
